metadata.name: Flying high
metadata.description:
Artist: Maurits Kool  
Editions: 1/1

Epic swell and some epic tricks shown in Lacanau France this summer. These locals put on a big show and I was at the right place at the right time. This was the most epic shot of the whole evening, a big air trick. Before you ask, he most definitely landed this, multiple times!
